      "message": "That\u0027s a good question.\n\nAFAIK Gerrit *should* always give revisions with no gaps, but I\u0027m not sure whether it\u0027s guaranteed. IMO it\u0027d probably be OK to not check this although it\u0027s an assumption that\u0027s worth noting",
